Class DelayAction

  • java.lang.Object

  • public class DelayAction
extends AbstractConditionalAction
    A useful AbstractConditionalAction for avoiding spam or kicking the player but not every time they flag a hack. This ONLY prevents the NEXT action from running, this is unique to only this action.

    imodm
